snippet.title: Bulletkour (Official Release Trailer)
snippet.description:
Bulletkour is a fast-paced action-parkour game based around using guns to propel yourself over obstacles, through enemies and across various different kinds of levels. Stay tuned on Steam!

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1996800/Bulletkour/
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/Yvs5NWNs4S
Twitter: https://twitter.com/studiovienas
Official website: https://studiovienas.com
